text: Steven Eugene Corino (born May 29, 1973) is a Canadian semi-retired professional wrestler. He is signed with WWE as a trainer and producer for their developmental territory NXT. He is best known for his time in Extreme Championship Wrestling (ECW) and Ring of Honor (ROH) under the ring name Steve Corino. He was born in Winnipeg, Manitoba. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian professional wrestlers Category:Professional wrestling managers and valets Category:Professional wrestling promoters Category:Sportspeople from Winnipeg
